##Submitting Poetry Responses in Microsoft Teams
We are using the Class Notebook feature in Microsoft Teams to submit homework responses during our poetry unit. Follow the steps below for help accessing the Class Notebook and for information on submitting homework responses.
Select the Teams page for your class.
Click on the Class Notebook link in the toolbar at the top of the Team page (Image 1). 
The Class Notebook will display a welcome screen. 
Click the symbol (>) to the left of the welcome screen message.
